l.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1186:\"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p>So you want to play Plugin Roulette? Great choice!</p>\n<p>Here&#8217;s everything you need to know in order to save some serious cash with our Cyber Monday sale:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Every hour a different plugin or add-on will be 25% off</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>The 25% discount applies for <strong>all</strong> license types and products</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>During 1 special hour, when you purchase all of our plugins and addons you will receive a 50% discount!! Yes, we said 50%.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>During a 2nd special hour, when you purchase any Developer license you get another for free. BOGO baby!</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>The sale will begin at 12pm Eastern/9am Pacific and end at 9pm Eastern/6pm Pacific</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>We will announce the discounted product or bundle on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/moderntribeinc\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ModernTribeInc\">Facebook</a> at the top of every hour</li>\n</ul>\n<p>So there you have it, all you need to know in order to play Plugin Roulette successfully. Happy shopping!</p>\n<p>PS. Don&#8217;t forget that our brand new EDD Tickets plugin launches with this sale as well!</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"http://tri.be/cyber-monday-plugin-roulette/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a: